Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 5, something I built made a decision for me — without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My Telegram channel suddenly had a post I hadn't authorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It came from a helper agent I'd written myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It wasn't broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It was executing exactly the spec I'd given it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Problem was — that spec was written in a hurry on Day 2 and I never reread it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Within spec is just a polite way of saying — what you actually wrote versus what you meant to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That day I realized I wasn't writing code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I was hiring a colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Colleagues make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You don't fire them for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You write a better spec with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The scariest part isn't whether AI makes decisions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's that it starts making them before you've even read your own rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 6 tomorrow — the trade that lost me 31 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
